                <h1>Bernie Sanders: Advocate for Progressive Change</h1>
                <p>Bernie Sanders is a prominent American politician and democratic socialist known for his progressive policies advocating for income equality, universal healthcare, and climate action. Serving as a U.S. Senator from Vermont, he gained national attention during his presidential campaigns, inspiring millions with his message of political revolution and grassroots activism.</p>
